    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Alprandus">Aliprando</name></persName> filio
                            <persName>bone memorie <name ref="Paulus de Vuamo"
                            >Pauli</name></persName>, de <placeName ref="#places/179"
                            >Vuamo</placeName>, permuta beni con <persName ref="#people/214"
                            key="#Bishops">Gherardus</persName>, gratia Dei huius sancte Lucane
                        ecclesie humilis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>. Aliprando cede a
                        Gherardo una petia de terra in loco et finibus
                            <placeName>Cassiano</placeName>, ubi dicitur Furnolo, qui capo uno tene
                        in terra eccl(esie) Sancte Marie, et alio lato tene in terra <persName><name
                                ref="Auderamus">Auderami</name></persName>, lato uno tene in <rs
                            key="#Roads">via publica</rs>, et alio capo tene in terra de ff. qd.
                        Alatei et in aliquantulum in terra Daiprandi diac; suprascriptam petiam de
                        terra (…) tota insimul est per mensura ad iusta pertica mensurata
                        sistariorum triginta sex et cum cesis et fossis suis (…) ad pars eccl(esie)
                        Sancte Marie (…). Riceve in cambio: una petia de terra illa in loco et
                        finibus Cassiano, prope Amiate, pertinentes suprascripte eccl(esie) Sancte
                        Marie sita loco Cassiano, que est de suppotestate ipsius epis(copatus)
                        vestro Sancti Martini, et est tenentes ipse terra uno capo in <rs
                            key="#Rivers">rivo Vuappao</rs>, et alio capo tene in terra et vinea
                        suprascripte eccl(esie) Sancte Marie, quas mihi menime dedisti, fini signa
                        et termina quas ibi posite sunt, lato uno tene in terra et vinea de ff. qd.
                        Alatei, et alio lato tene in terra et orto Auderami; suprascripta petia de
                        terra (…) est per mensura ad iusta pertica mensurata sistariorum viginti
                        septe, una cum cesis et sepis seu omnibus arboribus suis (…). Ubi et super
                        hanc comutationem tu qui supra <persName ref="#people/214"
                            key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities #Bishops">Gherardus</persName>
                        direxisti <rs key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities">missos tuos</rs>, hi
                        sunt <persName key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities #Deacons"><name
                                ref="Bertaldus">Bertaldus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diaconus</rs> filio <persName>bone memorie <name
                                ref="Helbulfus">Ilpolfi</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Richimundus">Richimundo</name></persName> filio <persName>bone
                            memorie <name ref="Lambertus">Lamperti</name></persName>, adque
                                <persName><name ref="Willeramus">Vuilleramo</name></persName> filio
                            <persName>bone memorie <name ref="Alateus">Alatei</name></persName>,
                        simulque <persName ref="#people/137"
                            key="#Count #Missus_of_other_public_authorities">Adalbertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comes</rs> direxit <rs
                            key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities">missos suos</rs>, hi sunt
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus/Ato">Petrus, que Ato</name>
                            vocatur</persName>, filio <persName>bone memorie <name ref="Richipertus"
                                >Richiperti</name></persName>, et <persName><name ref="Siculfus"
                                >Sicholfo</name></persName> filio <persName>bone memorie <name
                                ref="Ghisulfus">Ghisolfi</name></persName> seo Petrus notarius filio
                            <persName>bone memorie <name ref="Adalbrandus"
                            >Adalprandi</name></persName>, qui ambulaverunt ecc. cum alios bonos et
                        credente homines ecc. (…) Pena in duplum. <persName key="#Writer #Notary"
                                ><name ref="Gausbertus">Cospertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Churches #Mother_churches #Bishops"
                            >Luca</placeName>.</ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono i sei messi Bertaldus diaconus, Richimundo, Vuilleramo,
                        Petrus</ab>
